text: First off when you remember any mazes at all. You got by only left and right cause when you get to the forks unless there is multiple choices besides right or left straight isn't an option and either is down. This is because your always going to be facing straight or forward and unless there's stairs or something similar there is no down or up. However everyone remembers things a lil differently so what ever your process that helps you remember that works for you should be fine.  That being said I love watching Gura play games no matter what they are and even though she says she super scared she still continues to push forward never giving up witch is really cool cause some people can't do that. Madison? Just horror stings and extreme darkness.

I'd rather watch Gura play a horror game where she breaks it, like a VR game where you can phase through doors by bending out of bounds, than a no calories horror game. Hell, I'd love to see her continue that burger flipping horror game, it at least had comedy to its writing.
